&lt;h1 id="breaking-addiction-is-socially-unacceptable"&gt;Breaking Addiction Is Socially Unacceptable&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Feb 26 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Addiction enables artificial relationships and activities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
