&lt;h1 id="happiness-is-a-skill-you-can-develop"&gt;Happiness Is a Skill You Can Develop&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Feb 3 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&amp;rsquo;re not stuck at your current level of happiness&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first step to increasing your level of happiness is realizing you can. This is where a lot of people get tripped up. For the vast majority of people, some of their happiness—probably a lot more than they think—is in their control.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Happiness Without Material Comfort Is Playing on Hard Mode</title><link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/happiness-without-material-comfort-is-playing-on-hard-mode/</link><pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2020 21:29:41 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/happiness-without-material-comfort-is-playing-on-hard-mode/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/happiness-without-material-comfort-is-playing-on-hard-mode.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
