&lt;h1 id="happiness-without-material-comfort-is-playing-on-hard-mode"&gt;Happiness Without Material Comfort Is Playing on Hard Mode&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jan 29 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt; You can achieve happiness without financial wealth. Most of us recognize you&amp;rsquo;re not going to buy your way to happiness. But in modern times, you can buy your way out of common causes of unhappiness. Financial wealth can give you freedom and more time. It can give you peace.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>A Calm Mind, a Fit Body, a House Full of Love</title><link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/a-calm-mind-a-fit-body-a-house-full-of-love/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2019 19:22:57 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/a-calm-mind-a-fit-body-a-house-full-of-love/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/a-calm-mind-a-fit-body-a-house-full-of-love.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
